@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_czppzr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin(wp.exp(v0 + 0.21)))
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = (wp.cos(v2) * ((v1 + 0.83 * tmp + 0.96) / v0))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
